Yeah. Say hello.

54
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,759
Hello.

55
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:57,280
What are you doing?

56
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:59,400
Are you also here for the event?

57
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,480
Is that not allowed?

58
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,800
It's allowed.

59
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:05,919
Tian, slow down.

60
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:09,480
Johnny.

61
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,400
Slow down, Tian.

62
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,319
- Be careful. Are you okay?
- Thank you.

63
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:20,480
- Thank you, too. Are you here for the event?
- Yeah.

64
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,160
- Then let's go together.
- Okay.

65
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,920
There will also be many events

66
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:25,319
that you can participate in.

67
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,959
You can take a look.

68
00:04:26,959 --> 00:04:28,920
- Thanks a lot.
- Not at all.

69
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,959
Is that your son?

70
00:04:30,959 --> 00:04:32,720
No, he is my client.

71
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:34,279
I am the PR Manager at Xinghao.

72
00:04:34,279 --> 00:04:36,680
My name is Casey.

73
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:39,160
- Let's play together later.
- Sure.

74
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:41,864
Casey.

75
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:45,279
You guys at Xinghao are well-informed.

76
00:04:45,279 --> 00:04:48,480
I think you're also here
for Mrs. Liu's exhibition.

77
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,800
But that's no problem.

78
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:52,519
Afterwards, there are many
parent-child activities.

79
00:04:52,519 --> 00:04:53,560
It will depend on how well

80
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,720
you and your partner get along.

81
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,744
We'll find out soon.

82
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,360
Tian, go for it!

83
